-- Asya Katilim Bankasi to Seek Possible Buyers for Insurer Isik Sigorta
-- B y   A y d a n   E k s i n
-- 2010-11-12T05:28:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-12/asya-katilim-bankasi-to-seek-possible-buyers-for-insurer-isik-sigorta.html
Asya Katilim Bankasi AS, an Islamic
lender based in Istanbul, will examine strategic alternatives,
including a stake sale in its insurer unit Isik Sigorta.  Asya Katilim hired brokerage HSBC Yatirim as adviser to
seek and assess possible alternatives for Isik Sigorta, the bank
said in a statement to the Istanbul Stock Exchange yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aydan Eksin at 
 aeksin@bloomberg.net  